| accessdate=3 January 2007}}</ref> and was the first Indian celebrity included in the Celebrity version. Reportedly paid [[Rupee|Rs.]]31.5&nbsp;m (<U+00A3>367,500&nbsp;[[Pound sterling|GBP]]) for her participation,<ref name="moneyforBB7">{{cite web
| work=gg2.net
